Class GAMSSet

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.gams.api.GAMSSymbol<GAMSSetRecord>
      • com.gams.api.GAMSSet
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    java.lang.Iterable<GAMSSetRecord>

    public class GAMSSet
extends GAMSSymbol<GAMSSetRecord>
    This is the representation of a set symbol in GAMS. It exists in a GAMSDatabase and contains GAMSSetRecords which one can iterate through.
    See Also:
    GAMSDatabase, GAMSDatabase.addSet(String, int), GAMSDatabase.addSet(String, int, String), GAMSDatabase.addSet(String, String, Object...)
